OL,3,COperators cancel boat trips from
OL,4,CJersey to Herm due to travel rule
OL,6,FSome ferry companies have dropped
OL,7,Ftheir direct trips from to in response
OL,8,Fto travel rules.
OL,10,FBorder Agency has said it will enforce
OL,11,Fa "legal obligation" for boats to stop
OL,12,Fin an "approved port" such as St Peter
OL,13,FPort before visiting the island.
OL,15,FIt is in response to reports that a
OL,16,Fnumber of operators were not following
OL,17,Fthis law, which has been in place for
OL,18,Fseveral years to allow the necessary
OL,19,Fcustoms and immigration checks.
