OL,3,COperators cancel boat trips from
OL,4,CJersey to Herm due to travel rule
OL,6,FHowever, the Chief Executive of Herm
OL,7,FIsland, Craig Senior, believes it will
OL,8,Fdrive away daytrippers and have a big
OL,9,Fimpact on the local economy.
OL,11,FHe explained: "By enforcing this rule
OL,12,Ffor whatever reason we're losing a
OL,13,Fthousand guests, that will probably
OL,14,Flose us between five and ten thousand
OL,15,Fpounds.
OL,17,F"At this moment in time, there doesn't
OL,18,Fseem to be an appetite for Guernsey to
OL,19,Fwork with Jersey to allow guests to
OL,20,Fcome direct from Jersey to Herm."
